files.name: RYA enb319 1.31
files.changelogHtml: Edited some weather details:Light in night will be warmer and less bright. Increase the interior difference between the morning and the night(vigilant-coldharbour).Added a warmer palette to optional folder,dragging them into skyrim folder to get a warmer skyrim.You can see its effect in the latest screenshot

files.name: RYA enb319 1.4
files.changelogHtml: Correct interior color,it's too red before;adjust the lens effect to prevent sometimes overexposure;change the lightsprite parameters to make torch,candle,campfire and candlelight spell look good

files.name: RYA enb319 1.41
files.changelogHtml: *Update the optional WARM-Exterior palette.*Improved interior color and light.*Edited lens.fx for better performance.*Modified coast and reach weathers for a better scence

files.name: RYA enb319 1.5
files.changelogHtml: *Fixed the errors of esp file*Edited [SSAO_IL] and [SUBSURFACESCATTERING] parameters to enhance character's details

files.name: RYA enb319 1.51
files.changelogHtml: more bright eyes;improve fog and snow weathers' atmosphere;edit palette to decrease bright red or pink color ,make charater look more natural

files.name: RYA enb319 1.6
files.changelogHtml: Edited many weathers for better mist(or fog);improved clouds light and shadow

files.name: RYA enb319 1.62
files.changelogHtml: Fixed Reflection and EYES effect;edited enblocal.ini for stability;corrected some weathers

files.name: RYA enb319 1.7
files.changelogHtml: Now weather specific settings support Glenmoril and The Gary Cowl of Nocturnal；edited Adaptation parameters to make shadow place darker,it's too bright before.

files.name: RYA enb319 1.82
files.changelogHtml: Better performance;better skin manifestation;better DOF;better water;better palette and new optional colorful palette;now weather specific settings support Dragonborn
